---
const phases = [
	{
		name: 'Phase 1 · Safety foundation',
		items: [
			'Implement ShadowFileSystem service with staging + risk scoring.',
			'Ship ShadowModePanel UI for approving staged writes/deletes.',
			'Add IPC bridge so only the shadow system touches file:write/delete.',
		],
	},
	{
		name: 'Phase 2 · Liner architecture',
		items: [
			'Build the liner composition utility (`line()` + middleware typing).',
			'Package canonical liners: withShadowMode, withTelepathy, withBudget, withPolicy.',
			'Finalize createSafeNode factory so wrappers automatically receive liners.',
		],
	},
	{
		name: 'Phase 3 · Dynamic runtime',
		items: [
			'Initialize the Happen runtime inside the Electron renderer.',
			'Implement WorkbenchNode to compile + sandbox new tools.',
			'Create a generic CommandNode wrapper for system binaries.',
		],
	},
	{
		name: 'Phase 4 · State graph',
		items: [
			'Extend ContextGraphService with conversation nodes.',
			'Serialize only active nodes into the LLM prompt.',
			'Expose “Inbox item ⇄ Graph node” mapping for async reviews.',
		],
	},
];
---

<section class="border-b border-[hsl(var(--border))]/70 bg-[hsl(var(--background))]">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="space-y-4 text-center">
			<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]">
				Implementation checklist
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">
				A phased plan to upgrade Guru into an Agentic Harness.
			</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]">
				Each phase is shippable on its own. Teams often run Phases 1–2 in parallel (safety + liner architecture), introduce Workbench once governance is trusted,
				and finish by wiring the state graph into their LLM prompts.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2">
			{phases.map((phase) => (
				<div class="rounded-3xl border border-[hsl(var(--border))] bg-[hsl(var(--card))]/95 p-5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[hsl(var(--foreground))]">{phase.name}</h3>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]">
						{phase.items.map((item) => (
							<li class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[hsl(var(--primary))]"></span>
								<span>{item}</span>
							</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

